  <brief_title>Differentiation of Progression From Treatment Effects in High-Grade Gliomas: A Clinical Trial With Multimodality MR Imaging</brief_title>
  <official_title>Differentiation of Progression From Treatment Effects in High-Grade Gliomas: A Prospective Multicenter Clinical Trial With Multimodality MR Imaging</official_title>
