  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of multi-modality magnetic resonance quantitative parameters in
      evaluating the treatment effects of high-grade gliomas, and to provide new biomarkers for the
      establishment of new diagnostic criteria for the identification of true and pseudoprogression
      of high-grade gliomas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
